{"tid":1156933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜：當選總統後仍會留在高雄上班","createTime":"2019-05-16T02:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T04:03:13.000Z","uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d67b3b3bfad44e945c33d202facda844201a33d1","tid":1156933,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:19:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/不想初選-韓國瑜自己蓋總統府-090016364.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E7%91%9C%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E8%93%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%BA%9C-090016364.html&d=ljHbDMTA27iaUnmVhJlU2Kb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=608b6e09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/不想初選-韓國瑜自己蓋總統府-090016364.html</a><br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜受訪表示，當選總統後仍會留在高雄上班「不會跑了」，今日解釋，是為了平衡南北發展，資深媒體人尚毅夫在《94要客訴》直播政論節目上斷言，總統無法離開執掌或重大事情反應、指揮系統的重鎮，就算真的去高雄上班，可能會發現一星期也只有一天在高雄，其他六天在台北，他反問韓國瑜說，「難道只是晚上回家，飛回高雄嗎」。"},{"pid":"2dbf3d4e2fde9e7651ffdb6f17d38bd8a5821a3d","tid":1156933,"uid":156005,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"選到先講啦<br />\n參選政綱係咪得三隻字：發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12c7df3bff026a85431839d59db145fafb0bbe1","tid":1156933,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dbf3d4e2fde9e7651ffdb6f17d38bd8a5821a3d","tid":1156933,"uid":156005,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"選到先講啦<br />\n參選政綱係咪得三隻字：發大財<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:04:52.000Z","msg":"好難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4541c1bcc8bb6392dc2913e40448737f84e7bb1e","tid":1156933,"uid":188437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"大陸依家擺明降民調過去郭台銘,柯文哲去選<br />\n放長線睇下最後邊個出閘"},{"pid":"b207ae66fd46ed559e787d5361ae